phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common flow mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Not StateFlow | Use StateFlow |
| Heavy work in flow | Use Dispatchers.IO |
| Wrong scope | Use viewModelScope |
| No lifecycle | Use lifecycle-aware |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use StateFlow
private val _data = MutableStateFlow(emptyList<String>())

// 2. Use proper dispatcher
flow {
    withContext(Dispatchers.IO) {
        // Heavy work
    }
    emit(result)
}

// 3. Use viewModelScope
viewModelScope.launch { /* collect */ }

// 4. Use lifecycle-aware collect
LaunchedEffect(Unit) {
    viewModel.flow.collect { /* update */ }
}
```

